title: Teemo icon

replies.body: We're still sending icons out until **November 17th**. If you don't have it by then, please submit a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll help you out.
It can take up to 2 weeks *after* the Teemoing event ends (so up to November 17) for the icons to be added to your account. Just be patient and you will get receive the icons soon enough.
